Dealing {c_number}[SF_5]{/c} different types of Non-Physical damage increases the Potency of your Imbuement Skills by {c_number}[SF_9*100|%x|]{/c} for {c_number}[SF_3]{/c} seconds. 

This Potency is further increased by {c_number}[SF_8*100|%|]{/c} of the total amount of your Bonus damage to Poison, Shadow, and Cold. 

Current bonus: {c_number}[SF_0*100|%x|]{/c}.
